#: src/ui/app.rs:1478
msgid ""
"Here you can list your collected concerts. Via Import concerts you get an "
"overview of likely concerts: albums with live, unplugged or concert in the "
"name, plus single files of 30 minutes or more. Mark them as a concert and "
"they'll appear here. You can also add concerts later at any time via the "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Hapa unaweza kuorodhesha matamasha yako. Kupitia «Ingiza matamasha» unapata "
"muhtasari wa matamasha yanayowezekana: albamu zenye live, unplugged au "
"concert katika jina, pamoja na faili moja za dakika 30 au zaidi. Yaweke kama "
"tamasha nayo yataonekana hapa. Unaweza pia kuongeza matamasha wakati wowote "
"kupitia chaguo."

