#: src/ui/app.rs:1774
msgid ""
"YouTube isn't working right now – it changed and the installed yt-dlp can't "
"read it. Look for a newer version of the app or update yt-dlp in the "
"settings. If neither helps, please wait for a new yt-dlp release."
msgstr ""
"YouTube haifanyi kazi kwa sasa: imebadilika na yt-dlp iliyosakinishwa "
"haiwezi kuisoma. Tafuta toleo jipya la programu au sasisha yt-dlp katika "
"mipangilio. Ikiwa hakuna kinachosaidia, tafadhali subiri toleo jipya la yt-"
"dlp."

